The '''Cayan Club''' was an exclusive club on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] near the [[Rotunda Zone]] in the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], it was populated by fleet officers, [[Senator/Legends|senators]], and their ilk. [[Cha Niathal]] and [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] had intended to speak there when an explosion rocked Coruscant.

